             .contains(JDBCParameterMetaData.class.getName())\n+                        .contains(\"toStringImpl_exception\");\n+            }\n+        }\n+    }\n+\n+    private static Connection openConnection() throws Exception {\n+        return DriverManager.getConnection(\"jdbc:hsqldb:mem:parametermetadata\" + DATABASE_COUNTER.incrementAndGet(),\n+                \"SA\", \"\");\n+    }\n+}\n M metadata/org.hsqldb/hsqldb/2.4.1/reachability-metadata.json\n?? tests/src/org.hsqldb/hsqldb/2.4.1/src/test/java/org_hsqldb/hsqldb/JDBCParameterMetaDataTest.java\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777432624363}]}
